richLinkProperties.title: Sample Servant Sheet v2 - Ada Lovelace

textRun.content: Below is a list of skills that need special restrictions within the scope of Starry Night due to how easily they can be abused:

Due to the mass-produced nature of S.E.R.V.A.N.T. frames, each model can be tracked by the company that produced them. There are only two ways for a Servant to be off the grid: either by leaving a nomadic city and keeping out of range of its surveillance, or having Presence Concealment in their arsenal.

A Servant with Presence Concealment can hide the tracker in their Spirit Core from the system at their will. However, take caution, because any Servant that has gone offline for prolonged periods of time will be at risk for automatic deactivation by the system.

In order to keep fights fun for everyone involved, a Servant with any rank of Battle Continuation can only activate it once per Season. If you wish to use it multiple times in a Season, you’ll have to provide enough justification and/or tweak the skill into something else with similar flavors that fits the Servant’s legend.
